text: Doberman or Dobermann most commonly refers to Dobermann, a breed of dog. It may also refer to: *Doberman (album), a 2003 album by Tomoyasu Hotei *Doberman (band), a Japanese ska/punk band *"The Doberman", a song by Kasabian on their album Empire *Dobermann (film), a 1997 French film starring Vincent Cassel *Dobermann (surname) *Doberman-Yppan, a North American music publisher *Doberman Detective, a manga series and its feature film adaptation *Duane Doberman, a character from The Phil Silvers Show
title: Doberman (disambiguation)
